"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, Scotty here with Scotty's Fermented Foods. I want to talk to you today about my confetti relish. This is fermented cucumbers, onions, red bell peppers, pineapple, and apple. This is the only product I have that's a little bit sweet, a little bit sour. A lot of my products are sour and hot or just sour or you know, there's no sweetness in fermentation because that's what the bacteria are eating when you do ferment that. That's the process. But this one has a little bit of sweetness. This is a great way to try out fermented foods. A lot of us are kind of worried about oh, I might not like it. I know they're really good for you, but oh, I'm scared to lie, yeah, I don't know if I like sour stuff. This is what you start off with. This is your introduction to fermented foods. It's delicious. And it's a lot of basic flavors that a lot of us are more familiar with. And you can get it at Scotty'sfoods.com. Any four items gets you free shipping. Please order from me today. I'm a small business and I need your help. Thanks a ton.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, Scotty here with Scotty's Fermented Foods.\",\n      \"start\": 0.32,\n      \"end\": 3.28,\n      \"duration\": 2.96,\n      \"confidence\": 0.992,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.72,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 0.96,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n        